parameters: Clea (I have to go to the king's chamber...)
Clea (I have to go and meet with King Lex)

Clea: I'm sorry for keeping you waiting and causing you
trouble and worry.
Mage Relm: Is your body alright now?

Clea: There were no issues with my body. It's just that my
body has become a bit sluggish from sleeping for a whole
week.
Thief Nora: I didn't eat at all... Ugh, I was so worried!
Clea: I heard from the guild leader. Nice to meet you today.
Sister Eleo: Eek!? Ah, I'm fine, I'm completely fine!

Mage Relm: I don't understand why you're so nervous... I
want you to learn from the majestic figure of this genius!
Mage Relm: Your condition seems off... Are you really okay?

Thief Nora: It's a shame that Sophia-san couldn't come... I
wanted all of us to be praised by the queen if possible.
Clea: Please take care of Sophia-san's place for me.

Sister Eleo: P-Please leave it to me! It's a once-in-a-
lifetime audience, after all!

Sister Eleo: For Sophia-san, who couldn't come due to poor
health, I want to do my best to represent the village
properly...!
Clea: Then let's go to the king's chamber.
Fotizona Guard: This area is off-limits.

Fotizona Guardsman: We are conducting a hunt for remnants!
Please stay with King Rex, heroes!

Fotizona Guardsman: I apologize for the inconvenience, but
King Rex is currently undergoing repairs. Please proceed to
the King's Chamber and wait for him there.

Guild Leader Agonia: From here on, let's split up and
explore the inside of the royal palace.

Guild Leader Agonia: Clea and the others, please head
towards the rooftop through the right-hand corridor.

Guild Leader Agonia: There should be a dragon there, please
take care of that.

Clea: Leave the dragon to me. I will definitely stop Queen
Caron's ambition.

Swift Celis: 'Clea, let's definitely survive and meet
again.'
Clea: Of course, at the Adventurer's Guild again!
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Prince Rex: It's not over yet, but thanks to that, the
biggest problem has been resolved.

Prince Rex: Thanks to all of you, I will formally invite you
to the royal palace at a later date.

Prince Rex: I will declare the subjugation of Caron in front
of the royal palace. I want all of you to come with me.
Prince Rex: Now, the soldiers are waiting.

Fotizona Guardsman: We are conducting a hunt for remnants!
Please stay with King Rex, heroes!

Fotizona Guardsman: We are conducting a hunt for remnants!
Please stay with King Rex, heroes!

Fotizona Guardsman: I apologize for the inconvenience, but
King Rex is currently undergoing repairs. Please proceed to
the King's Chamber and wait for him there.
Clea: The scars of battle still remain, don't they?

Mage Relm: King Rex didn't have to invite us to the royal
palace in such a hurry, did he?

Priestess Sophia: It seems like you're already very busy, so
I suppose that's why we were called here now...

Priestess Sophia: Oh, Nora-chan, is there something
bothering you?

Thief Nora: I feel like I'm forgetting something... Hmm...
I'll let you know once I remember!
Clea: Well then, let's go meet King Rex.
